Package org.odpi.openmetadata.integrationservices.lineage.properties

Class OpenLineageOutputDataSetOutputFacets

java.lang.Object
org.odpi.openmetadata.integrationservices.lineage.properties.OpenLineageOutputDataSetOutputFacets
public class OpenLineageOutputDataSetOutputFacets extends Object
This class represents the map of output facets in the open lineage standard spec https://github.com/OpenLineage/OpenLineage/blob/main/spec/OpenLineage.json.
